wordpressPost.title: Rimmel Stay Matte Powder Review
wordpressPost.content:
Rimmel Stay Matte Powder Review

 

I have used so many powders on my face.  I like Estee Lauder, Clinique, Rhianna, and a few others.  I used these for years.  But, they can get costly.  Just recently, I ran out of powder and ran into Walgreens and found Rimmel Stay Matte Powder for only five bucks!

I figured I didn’t have much to lose so I bought this powder and it was amazing!  Especially for the price.
